c: 7
v: 37
t: "And who is worse than he who deviseth a lie of God, or treateth our signs as lies? To them shall a portion here below be assigned in accordance with the Book of our decrees, until the time when our messengers, as they receive their souls, shall say, \"Where are they on whom ye called beside God?\" They shall say: \"Gone from us.\" And they shall witness against themselves that they were infidels"